snippet.textDisplay:
Cooked the meat chili today. What an awful, awful idea. It made a good looking paper towel ad, but the worst “chili” recipe I’ve tasted. Disgusting.

3 hours of simmering and the dried pepper paste still can be made out when you taste it....like oily, waxy wrapping paper pieces.
